| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0001 — Recovery Inhibition (coinbasecartel)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c37a5228-adea-5da1-8047-54d14e22cb6a"
